&lt;p&gt;Serve as Sage’s primary clinical partner for SNF customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain trusted relationships with Directors of Nursing, Administrators, regional clinical leaders, and frontline staff&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and develop clinical champions and convert skeptics into advocates through hands-on partnership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead regular clinical engagement cadences across pilot and expansion sites&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent Sage’s clinical expertise in enterprise conversations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
