&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operate and improve critical data infrastructure&lt;/strong&gt;, ensuring high availability, performance, backup strategies, and disaster recovery processes for production databases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead capacity planning and auto-scaling efforts&lt;/strong&gt;, ensuring infrastructure and systems scale effectively as product usage grows.&lt;/li&gt;
